description: This stunning 2 bed 2 bath spread over 1487 sqft on a single floor is ready for entertaining! The boutique building has 9 units. The living room is drenched in natural light from the massive floor to ceiling windows. The kitchen is fit for a chef with Wolf stove, Sub Zero refrigerator, wine fridge, pot filler and abundant counter and cabinet space. The bedrooms can both fit king sized beds and have a ton of closet space. The primary bath is complete with steam shower. Take the elevator to the common roof deck to enjoy an al fresco dinner or take in the summer sun on one of the chaise lounges. The unit is spectacular and the location is A+. Just minutes from Rt 93, Rt 90, Broadway T, South Boston Waterfront and close proximity to restaurants, Castle Island, and more! This amazing opportunity will not last. Come get settled before Summer!
